text.div:
This code system http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/CodeSystem/match-method defines the following codes:

CodeDisplay
automated Automoted matching algorithm or model identified the match
manual Manual matching performed by a human
none No match was performed or identifed

name: MatchMethodCodeSystem
title: Match Method Codes
description: Codes indicating methods used to identify matched entities

concept.display: Automoted matching algorithm or model identified the match
Manual matching performed by a human
No match was performed or identifed
